articles.headline: Westbrook cashes in on a quick jam
articles.description: Andre Roberson blocks and strips the ball away from Wesley Matthews and hits an open Russell Westbrook for the quick slam.

images.name: Westbrook cashes in on a quick jam
images.caption: Andre Roberson blocks and strips the ball away from Wesley Matthews and hits an open Russell Westbrook for the quick slam.

articles.headline: Curry breaks cold streak from deep
articles.description: Steph Curry hits a 3-pointer after missing his first eight attempts vs. the Pelicans.

images.name: Curry breaks cold streak from deep
images.caption: Steph Curry hits a 3-pointer after missing his first eight attempts vs. the Pelicans.

articles.headline: Harden leads Rockets to 117-102 win over Knicks
articles.description: James Harden had 37 points and 10 assists as the Houston Rockets rallied from an early deficit to beat the New York Knicks 117-102 on Saturday night.

images.name: Nene throws down one-handed slam
images.caption: Nene drives to the basket and gets a big one-handed slam for the Rockets.

articles.headline: Irving, Horford lead Celtics to 108-98 win at Indiana
articles.description: Kyrie Irving scored 25 points and Al Horford added 21 to lead the Boston Celtics to a 108-98 victory over the Indiana Pacers on Saturday night.

images.name: Stephenson headbutts after driving dunk
images.caption: Lance Stephenson throws down a strong jam in the first quarter and celebrates by headbutting the padding for the basket.

articles.headline: Bledsoe takes the hit and drains two
articles.description: Eric Bledsoe manages to get the layup to fall while taking contact and drawing the foul.

images.name: Bledsoe takes the hit and drains two
images.caption: Eric Bledsoe manages to get the layup to fall while taking contact and drawing the foul.

articles.headline: Raptors dominate Hawks
articles.description: Kyle Lowry records a double-double of 15 points and 13 rebounds as seven Toronto players score in double digits en route to a 112-78 win.

images.name: Raptors dominate Hawks
images.caption: Kyle Lowry records a double-double of 15 points and 13 rebounds as seven Toronto players score in double digits en route to a 112-78 win.
